The paper focuses on natural language understanding and proposes a novel framework for cloze-style reading comprehension. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques and proposes a sampling mechanism, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
